_sText:
Practice your aim with the AK

when you join shoot the yellow button on the left to start the targets

the first round is a warm up practice round

once it has finished you then shoot the yellow button again

This will now start the targets again but from now on there is a limited time to shoot the targets.

once the round has finished you can look to the right and see how many targets you have hit /missed

keep practicing and it will help your aim with the AK

you need to save ammo and minimise reloads or the time will run out quickly
